Users Workflows

Tutors
  Homepage:
    Introduction
    Demo
    Subscriptions Plans, Add On
    Login
    Register with Oauth

  Logined Dashboard:
    Add classroom
    Classrooms(List of Classrooms)
    Settings
    Calendar
    Subscription Plans and Available Add On: 1) Screen Lock, 2) AI hints and feedback (Plans, Add On can be added and edited on Admin page)
    Terms of Use of Teachers and Disclaimer

  Classroom Dashboard:
    Teacher Google Drive Folder Permission and URL setup:
    Start the Classroom
    Add students
    Students: 
      name | student email | parent email | screen locked? | send email when leaving focus? | send lesson report? | save materials into Student Google Drive Folder? | remark: eg. strength, weakness, personality
      All student default settings are NIL. If one attribute is set, it will override the class setting on this student
    Time: Date and Time, Frequency, Duration, Last Date(can be N/A)
    Scope: Subject, Student major age, Major Country, Major Province or City, Major Language
    Class Settings: All Student screen locked?, Video On? Audio Off?, Send email when leaving focus?, Send lesson report?, Save materials into Student Google Drive Folder?, Send Tuition Fee reminder Email to parents?, Send Next Day Lesson reminder Email to students?, Send Next Day Homework Deadline reminder Email to students?, Use AI hints and feedback?
      Remarks: [Screen Lock, AI hints and feedback] are add on. If tutor hasn't subscribe these add on and they select these options, route them to add on subscription page
    

  Settings:
    Country:
    Province or City:
    Language:
    Send Lesson Reminder Email to themselves?


  Subscription Plans:
    Support US$, CAD$, UK$, EURO$, YUAN$, HK$, YEN$, AUST$
    All prices of other currencies should be converted from US$ automatically

    Free Plan:
      Hour limit per month: 55 minutes
      Screen Lock limit: 30 minutes
      Send lesson reports limit: 1 lesson
      AI hints and feedback: 30 minutes

    Standard Plan: US$11.9 monthly, US$119.9 annually
      Time limit per month: 100 hours
      Screen Lock limit: 120 minutes
      Send lesson reports limit: No limit
      AI hints and feedback: 120 minutes
      Screen Lock Add On No Limit: US$4
      AI feedback Add On No Limit: US$8

    Premium Plan: US$19.9 monthly, US$199.9 annually
      Time limit per month: 200 hours
      Screen Lock limit: 240 minutes
      Send lesson reports limit: No limit
      AI hints and feedback: 240 minutes
      Screen Lock Add On No Limit: US$7
      AI feedback Add On No Limit: US$15

    Enterprise Plan: US$179.9 monthly, US$1699.9 annually
      Teachers: 10
      Time limit per month: 200 hours
      Screen Lock limit: 240 minutes
      Send lesson reports limit: No limit
      AI hints and feedback: 240 minutes
      Screen Lock Add On No Limit: US$60
      AI feedback Add On No Limit: US$140



Students
  Login Page: basic information of the platform

  Logined dashboard:
